{"tid":1643422,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"波波教練被大陸網民詛咒早日與亡妻相聚","createTime":"2019-10-10T06:20:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T06:36:12.000Z","uid":89543,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c7739732ac8158ceb2e49f0360abdfbc252ca8fc","tid":1643422,"uid":89543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T06:20:02.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕火箭隊總管莫雷（Daryl Morey）發推特挺香港反送中，導致中國官、民對NBA強烈不滿。對此，馬刺名教練帕波維奇（Gregg Popovich）受訪時力挺NBA總裁席爾瓦（Adam Silver）的「言論自由」說。沒想到竟有大量中國在網路上留言「祝帕波維奇早日與他的妻子相聚」，而帕波維奇的愛妻已於去年4月過世。"},{"pid":"a2c40548f2e023d6cf6daeb58e3a63c36f681674","tid":1643422,"uid":89543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T06:20:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12adce649ee5380124728fde51dc67d14d35bb37","tid":1643422,"uid":69472,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T06:36:12.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母<br />\n鬧波波"}]}